title: 820-00923 no Wi-Fi
message:
I've got an 820-00923 with no Wi-Fi. AHT confirms the no Wi-Fi but this machine is newer than what I typically work on so I'm not sure where to start. No liquid damage, no other damage. Machine works great except Wi-Fi. Any pointers? :)

Looking at the schematic there is a lot more involved with the Wi-Fi than prior years/models. Figured the first thing I'm looking for is an enable or power line but having a hard time finding it.

title: 820-00923 no Wi-Fi
message:
No hardware installed in System Report, for WiFi?
Check power rails for U3730.

title: 820-00923 no Wi-Fi
message: This was picked up before I could further investigate, can be marked as closed. Thanks for the help 2informaticos
